Modules

AuthModule (JWT, refresh, email verify).
UsersModule, CraftsmenModule, CatalogModule.
SearchModule (geo queries, ranking).
AvailabilityModule (rules, slots, calendar service).
AppointmentsModule (lifecycle, policies, SLA timers).
WalletModule (ledger, holds, capture, payouts) + PaymobModule (webhooks, signatures).
ReviewsModule, MessagingModule (WS gateway), NotificationsModule.
SubscriptionsModule, AdminModule, DisputesModule.
JobsModule (BullMQ queues: emails, reminders, settlement, cleanup).

Cross-Cutting

Pipes & Guards: ValidationPipe, AuthGuard, RolesGuard.
Interceptors: Logging, Caching, Sentry.
Config: @nestjs/config with env validation; secrets from Vault